    "night": "After dinner \u2014 usually home-cooked food with plenty of spices and vegetables \u2014 Arvind spends time reading academic papers, Indigenous histories, or fiction with political themes. He likes to end his day meditating briefly, reflecting on both personal goals and broader social issues before heading to bed around midnight."
